<cb:div>
<pb n="0088a" xml:id="I01.0035.0088a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 35</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0088a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>張法壽息榮遷等造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0088a00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之一　碑側</cb:mulu><head>之一　碑側</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0088a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0088a0101">夫靈真玄廓。妙絕難測。非言莫能宣其<note n="0088001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𣅀＝旨【史】</note><note n="0088001" resp="ihp" type="mod">𣅀【佛拓】，旨【史】</note><app n="0088001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">旨</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𣅀</rdg></app>。非像無以表其狀。言宣二六
<lb ed="I" n="0088a02" type="honorific"/>之教。像跡四八之<note n="0088002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30605"/>＝璃【史】</note><note n="0088002" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30605"/>【佛拓】，璃【史】</note><app n="0088002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30605"/></rdg></app>。豈不淵玄<note n="0088003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">冲＝沖【史】</note><note n="0088003" resp="ihp" type="mod">冲【佛拓】，沖【史】</note><app n="0088003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">沖</lem><rdg wit="【原】">冲</rdg></app>漠。巍巍惟極者哉。是以務聖寺檀主
<lb ed="I" n="0088a03" type="honorific"/>張法壽。能於五蓋重羅之下。<note n="0088004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𢍆＝契【史】</note><note n="0088004" resp="ihp" type="mod">𢍆【佛拓】，契【史】</note><app n="0088004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">契</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𢍆</rdg></app>斷<note n="0088005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30606"/>＝恩【史】</note><note n="0088005" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30606"/>【佛拓】，恩【史】</note><app n="0088005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">恩</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30606"/></rdg></app>愛塵勞之繒網。於熙平二年。捨宅
<lb ed="I" n="0088a04" type="honorific"/>造寺。宿願磛像。福不止已。<note n="0088006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">䂓＝規【史】</note><note n="0088006" resp="ihp" type="mod">䂓【佛拓】，規【史】</note><app n="0088006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">規</lem><rdg wit="【原】">䂓</rdg></app>度法界。尋其羅絡。情苞聖境。自非藉因積
<lb ed="I" n="0088a05" type="honorific"/>劫。英貴累世者。熟能發茲宏闊願行者焉。息榮遷。脩和。行慈仁孝。世習
<lb ed="I" n="0088a06" type="honorific"/>精<note n="0088007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30607"/>＝懿【史】</note><note n="0088007" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30607"/>【佛拓】，懿【史】</note><app n="0088007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">懿</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30607"/></rdg></app>。志慕幽寂。妙真遐願。刊石建像。釋迦文佛。觀音。文殊。仰述亡考。平
<lb ed="I" n="0088a07" type="honorific"/>康<note n="0088008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30608"/>＝舊【史】</note><note n="0088008" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30608"/>【佛拓】，舊【史】</note><app n="0088008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30608"/></rdg></app>願。復於像側。隱出<note n="0088a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">无【CB】，旡【原】【史】</note><app n="0088a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">无</lem><rdg wit="【原】【史】">旡</rdg></app>量壽佛。福洽法界。考妣等神。捨茲質形。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">悉</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0088a08" type="honorific"/><note n="0088009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30609"/>＝稟【史】</note><note n="0088009" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30609"/>【佛拓】，稟【史】</note><app n="0088009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">稟</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30609"/></rdg></app>淨境。同<note n="0088010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30610"/>＝曉【史】</note><note n="0088010" resp="ihp" type="mod"><g ref="#CB30610"/>【佛拓】，曉【史】</note><app n="0088010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">曉</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30610"/></rdg></app>薩雲。覺道成佛。
<lb ed="I" n="0088a09" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　大魏天平二年歲次乙卯四月十一日比丘洪寶銘</p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b00" type="honorific"/><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">之二　碑陰</cb:mulu><head>之二　碑陰</head>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0088b0101">
<lb ed="I" n="0088b02" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b03" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b04" type="honorific"/>金山寶蓋如來　范定洛南方寶相如來　文殊師利佛主張義容　普光佛主毛元姜　大通智勝佛主衛僧副　帝相佛主尹文敬為父母　寶華功德海琉<app type="star" corresp="#0088002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30605"/></rdg></app>金山光明如來主寇令容
<lb ed="I" n="0088b05" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b06" type="honorific"/>金炎光明如來　車河興東方阿閦如來　阿彌陀佛主董元士　日月燈明佛主楊塔　須彌頂佛張仲華為父母梵相佛主楊聖鬘　光明如來主曹佛光
<lb ed="I" n="0088b07" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b08" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b09" type="honorific"/>光明王相如來主張桃奉寶勝如來奉為父母　　　　　　　　　　　藥師琉<app type="star" corresp="#0088002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">璃</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30605"/></rdg></app>光佛楊元寄　師子音佛主宋文勝　多摩羅跋栴檀香神通佛名相如來二佛主榮千
<lb ed="I" n="0088b10" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b11" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b12" type="honorific"/>无垢熾寶如來主曇景　寶相如來主權荊珍　釋迦多寶二佛范<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">佛</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">保</unclear>　難勝佛張遵為父母　虛空住佛主田貴洛　須彌相佛董龍國為父母閻浮那提金光如來
<lb ed="I" n="0088b13" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b14" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b15" type="honorific"/>難勝如來主僧真　大炬如來主咎寄保　北微妙聲佛崔進合家　觀世音佛主劉道亮　常滅佛　　　　　　　　雲自在佛董歸樂為母　多摩羅跋旃檀香佛
<lb ed="I" n="0088b16" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b17" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088b18" type="honorific"/>□□如來主惠照　金華炎光<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">相</unclear>如來主田佛光　西无量<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">壽</unclear>．．．．<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">那</unclear>佛主段崑崙　華光佛主路法奴<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雲</unclear>　自在王佛段邕為亡息鼠兒　寶藏佛張世伯為亡母</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div>
<lb ed="I" n="0088c01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0088c0101">董大醜
<lb ed="I" n="0088c02" type="honorific"/>董清頭
<lb ed="I" n="0088c03" type="honorific"/>董夏歡
<lb ed="I" n="0088c04" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088c05" type="honorific"/>願元王崇禮兄弟
<lb ed="I" n="0088c06" type="honorific"/>五人悉得善集大
<lb ed="I" n="0088c07" type="honorific"/>家范度內外七世
<lb ed="I" n="0088c08" type="honorific"/>父母法界倉生成佛
<lb ed="I" n="0088c09" type="honorific"/>張榮千為存亡二
<lb ed="I" n="0088c10" type="honorific"/>弟南方字榮和
<lb ed="I" n="0088c11" type="honorific"/>身康常貴亡者
<lb ed="I" n="0088c12" type="honorific"/>遇佛法界成佛
<lb ed="I" n="0088c13" type="honorific"/>張桃棒造二佛
<lb ed="I" n="0088c14" type="honorific"/>一佛為亡父母<app type="star" corresp="#0088008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">舊</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30608"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0088c15" type="honorific"/>願造一佛為法
<lb ed="I" n="0088c16" type="honorific"/>界眾生一切父母
<lb ed="I" n="0088c17" type="honorific"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0088c18" type="honorific"/></p>
</cb:div>
</cb:div>
